latestPosts.caption:
This Rust Farshi salwar suit perfect for intimate weddings, bridal trousseau, festive dinners, or just those days when you want to feel extra special.
Crafted in pure fabric and detailed with zardozi embroidery, it’s a timeless piece every bride-to-be needs in her wardrobe.

I styled it with:
• A statement golden clutch
• Statement golden heels
• Silver polki jhumkis from @amethystbyrahulpopli
 • A silver moissanite polki maangtikka from the same label
• And a classic, sleek bun to complete the look

Trust me, this look is effortless royalty.

@amethaveli
